---
// Decorative-only: film grain + aurora blobs. Sits above the body
// background, below all real content. aria-hidden so screen readers
// don't announce decorative noise.
---
<div class="grain" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<div class="aurora" aria-hidden="true">
  <span class="aurora-blob aurora-blob-1"></span>
  <span class="aurora-blob aurora-blob-2"></span>
  <span class="aurora-blob aurora-blob-3"></span>
</div>
